import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import "./styles/GrowthTable.css"; const GrowthTable = ({ character, gameClass, expertise, starsphere }) => { const characterName = character.name; const gameClassName = gameClass.name; const growthTotals = { hp: character.hp + gameClass.hp, str: 10, mag: 10, dex: 10, spd: 10, def: 10, res: 10, lck: 10, bld: 10, } return (
Character Stats Base Class Starsphere Expertise TOTAL
{characterName} | {gameClassName} HP {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.hp: 0} {growthTotals.hp}
STR {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.str: 0} {growthTotals.str}
MAG {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.mag: 0} {growthTotals.mag}
DEX {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.dex: 0} {growthTotals.dex}
SPD {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? "True": 0} {growthTotals.spd}
DEF {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.def: 0} {growthTotals.def}
RES {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.res: 0} {growthTotals.res}
LCK {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.lck: 0} {growthTotals.lck}
BLD {starsphere? 15 : 0} {expertise? gameClass.bld: 0} {growthTotals.bld}
) } export default GrowthTable;
